							<img src="./assets/images/icon/icon-info-type5.svg" alt="" class="library-facility-section__icon" />
							<h3 class="library-facility-section__title">층별현황</h3>
						</div>
						<div class="scroll-x">
							<table class="facility-table">
								<colgroup>
									<col style="width: 120px;" />
									<col style="width: 150px;" />
									<col style="width: 100px;" />
									<col style="width: auto;" />
								</colgroup>
								<thead>
									<tr>
										<th>층별</th>
										<th>실명</th>
										<th>좌석수</th>
										<th>내용</th>
									</tr>
								</thead>
								<tbody>
									<tr>
										<td rowspan="6">지상1층</td>
										<td>안내데스크</td>
										<td>-</td>
										<td class="text-left">도서관 이용안내, 대출반납, 회원가입 등</td>
									</tr>
									<tr>
										<td>어린이자료실</td>
										<td>-</td>
										<td class="text-left">유아·아동 총류(000) ~ 역사(900) 자료실, 아동 정기간행물</td>
									</tr>
									<tr>
										<td>유아가족실</td>
										<td>4석</td>
										<td class="text-left">영·유아 총류(000) ~ 역사(900) 자료실</td>
									</tr>
									<tr>
										<td>수유실</td>
										<td>-</td>
										<td class="text-left">영아 수유실</td>
									</tr>
									<tr>
										<td>창의놀이공간</td>
										<td>15석</td>
										<td class="text-left">창의놀이 프로그램 진행</td>
									</tr>
									<tr>
										<td>프로그램실 1</td>
										<td>12석</td>
